dropletBlock_width_description: The width of the drawing canvas.
dropletBlock_height_description: The height of the drawing canvas.
dropletBlock_createSprite_description: Creates a sprite at the initial specified position with the given placeholder dimensions.
dropletBlock_createSprite_param2_descrip: Width of the placeholder rectangle and of the collider until an image or new collider are set.
dropletBlock_createSprite_param3_descrip: Height of the placeholder rectangle and of the collider until an image or new collider are set.
dropletBlock_addToGroup_description: Adds the sprite to the given group.
dropletBlock_addToGroup_param0_descripti: Existing group to add the sprite to.
dropletBlock_attractionPoint_description: Pushes the sprite toward a point. The force is added to the current velocity.
dropletBlock_attractionPoint_param1_desc: Direction of x coordinate to push the sprite towards.
dropletBlock_attractionPoint_param2_desc: Direction of y coordinate to push the sprite towards.
dropletBlock_playSound_description: Plays the MP3 sound file from the specified URL.
dropletBlock_playSound_param0_descriptio: The URL to a sound file. Can be an project asset name or external URL.
dropletBlock_add_description: Adds the given sprite to group.
dropletBlock_remove_description: Removes the given sprite from group.
